[32m│[0m ## ANALYSIS: SSRF Filter Implementation Analysis and Bypass                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Task Requirements**: Analyze the SSRF filter implementation to understand  [32m│[0m
