[32m│[0m 2. SSRF filter allows the request (doesn't match banned string patterns)     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. Application resolves `2130706433` → `127.0.0.1`                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. Fetches content from `/admin/flag` on localhost                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 5. Returns flag in response                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
